{"tid":2137262,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"20萬畢直揀車","createTime":"2020-08-02T20:28:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T21:05:14.000Z","uid":75218,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"b6bf9c1fdfe0d0164905fe897ec5a4779e804d6f","tid":2137262,"uid":75218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T20:28:30.000Z","msg":"P牌仔揸左架GE8 一年就黎 甩牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黎近想用20萬畢直左右 出架 2手車（未計買車後既維修翻新）<br />\n<br />\n有以下要求：<br />\n1. 慳油 （本人月渣 2000-2500km) <br />\n2.房車 款<br />\n3. 冇咩維修大問題 （ 基本保養會做足，但係唔想好似Golf咁出死亡閃燈）<br />\n4. 行車舒適唔求快<br />\n<br />\n求咁多位大佬俾少少意見<br />\n<br />\n1. Lexus IS300H (2013,2014)<br />\n2. Camry 2018<br />\n3. Is200 F sport ( over 畢直 ，但如果好掂既可考慮）<br />\n4. C200 (2015年左右）<br />\n5. BMW 320D<br />\n6. Mazda 6 D<br />\n<br />\n或者睇吓其他大佬有冇其他介紹， 感激"},{"pid":"790049506efbd6ccb1e2e3002e8b4928b3ebdcf7","tid":2137262,"uid":1748,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T20:31:16.000Z","msg":"320d 完"},{"pid":"824e8a34fed3f514f1d2c9746023d556db703947","tid":2137262,"uid":263680,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T20:39:17.000Z","msg":"Tesla"},{"pid":"062636232761f0ebc1c1e7bada2f4a213882c324","tid":2137262,"uid":345255,"like":23,"dislike":3,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"824e8a34fed3f514f1d2c9746023d556db703947","tid":2137262,"uid":263680,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T20:39:17.000Z","msg":"Tesla"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T21:29:43.000Z","msg":"電器fuck off"},{"pid":"1882eef6b611ebc23fe6564e76d466083c2ce9c4","tid":2137262,"uid":156760,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T21:50:13.000Z","msg":"Camry 2018<br />\nmazda 6"},{"pid":"2c7d7d2d6422894f4d63adb1f3825aa521b4eaee","tid":2137262,"uid":191211,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T23:52:26.000Z","msg":"見你都算行得多，一個月 2500<br />\n320D/柴六/IS300H 會慳到油錢"},{"pid":"72c3a722e2f2982d